IWLCA Celebrates 2024 Division II All-American Teams

48 student-athletes honored

 

The IWLCA has announced the 48 student-athletes selected for the 2024 Division II All-American teams, divided into first, second, and third teams. These IWLCA All-Americans, representing 23 different institutions, are recognized as the top athletes in the sport this year.
